In the INTEREST OF S.W., Minor Child, K.P., Mother, Petitioner-Appellee, E.W., Father, Respondent-Appellant. No. 18-1356 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 17, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904
